[thinking] **Analyzing JaCoCo coverage**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m looking into why JaCoCo is showing a class method as not covered when the test results passed. Maybe it’s because that method is excluded or related to synthetic methods? I think inspecting the JaCoCo HTML report might be helpful.
