[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering why Class.forName might not be capturing coverage as expected. Could it be that native substitution is folding it into a constant? Maybe using class$ with a class name that isn’t reachable plays a role, but does it really need dynamic metadata?
[thinking] 
